Problem 3: flow_steps_train: 8 — Unnecessary GPU Cost
Each gradient step ran the flow ODE 8 times forward. Since you're fine-tuning from a pretrained IQL checkpoint, not training from scratch, 4 steps gives nearly identical gradient quality at half the compute cost.
